WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:02.500
Is it right?

2
00:00:03.266 --> 00:00:05.466
I admit that I am your father

3
00:00:05.466 --> 00:00:09.966
I was the one who abandoned you 15 years ago

4
00:00:10.366 --> 00:00:11.700
And he sold your kidney

5
00:00:12.333 --> 00:00:13.566
Me too.

6
00:00:14.100 --> 00:00:15.900
Drag you into the wilderness

7
00:00:16.166 --> 00:00:17.866
I want to kill you with my own hands

8
00:00:18.266 --> 00:00:20.066
I am not human

9
00:00:20.300 --> 00:00:21.633
I am an animal

10
00:00:21.700 --> 00:00:23.266
I will not be your father

11
00:00:27.100 --> 00:00:28.266
It's really you?

12
00:00:28.566 --> 00:00:30.833
I had a huge gambling debt.

13
00:00:31.466 --> 00:00:32.400
penniless

14
00:00:32.566 --> 00:00:34.466
Your mother ran away with someone else

15
00:00:34.466 --> 00:00:38.366
I take you everywhere to hide debts, not enough to eat, not enough to wear

16
00:00:38.366 --> 00:00:41.833
It just so happens that Shi always wants to do a kidney transplant for Young Master Su

17
00:00:42.166 --> 00:00:45.100
Your kidney is a good match for Young Master Su

18
00:00:45.533 --> 00:00:47.600
So I don't do it.

19
00:00:49.133 --> 00:00:51.100
That's why I sold your kidney to Mr. Su

20
00:00:51.100 --> 00:00:53.066
Took the money and paid off the gambling debt

21
00:00:53.333 --> 00:00:55.466
I have been working with Mr. Su since then

22
00:00:55.700 --> 00:00:58.200
That's it, that's it

